实现基于 DAG 依赖层级的自动阶段划分算法。

## 核心算法

### assignPhases(knowledgePoints, dependencyGraph)

主函数，负责整个阶段划分流程：

```javascript
function assignPhases(knowledgePoints, dependencyGraph) {
  // 1. 计算每个节点的拓扑层级
  const levels = computeTopologicalLevels(dependencyGraph);

  // 2. 根据层级数量决定阶段数量
  const maxLevel = Math.max(...Object.values(levels));
  const phaseCount = Math.min(maxLevel + 1, 5); // 最多5个阶段

  // 3. 将层级映射到阶段（合并相邻层级）
  const levelsPerPhase = Math.ceil((maxLevel + 1) / phaseCount);

  knowledgePoints.forEach(kp => {
    const level = levels[kp.id];
    kp.phase = Math.floor(level / levelsPerPhase) + 1;
  });

  // 4. 生成阶段元数据
  const phases = [];
  for (let i = 1; i <= phaseCount; i++) {
    const kpsInPhase = knowledgePoints.filter(kp => kp.phase === i);
    phases.push({
      phase_number: i,
      phase_name: getPhaseNameByNumber(i, phaseCount),
      knowledge_point_ids: kpsInPhase.map(kp => kp.id),
      description: generatePhaseDescription(i, phaseCount, kpsInPhase),
      status: i === 1 ? 'active' : 'locked'
    });
  }

  return { knowledgePoints, phases };
}
```

### computeTopologicalLevels(dependencyGraph)

使用 BFS 计算每个节点的层级：

```javascript
function computeTopologicalLevels(graph) {
  const levels = {};
  const inDegree = {};
  const queue = [];

  // 初始化入度
  graph.nodes.forEach(node => {
    inDegree[node] = 0;
    levels[node] = 0;
  });

  graph.edges.forEach(edge => {
    inDegree[edge.to]++;
  });

  // 找到所有入度为0的节点（根节点）
  graph.nodes.forEach(node => {
    if (inDegree[node] === 0) {
      queue.push(node);
    }
  });

  // BFS 遍历
  while (queue.length > 0) {
    const current = queue.shift();
    const currentLevel = levels[current];

    // 处理所有出边
    graph.edges
      .filter(edge => edge.from === current)
      .forEach(edge => {
        const next = edge.to;
        levels[next] = Math.max(levels[next], currentLevel + 1);
        inDegree[next]--;

        if (inDegree[next] === 0) {
          queue.push(next);
        }
      });
  }

  return levels;
}
```

### getPhaseNameByNumber(num, total)

根据阶段数量生成合适的阶段名称：

```javascript
function getPhaseNameByNumber(num, total) {
  if (total <= 3) {
    return ['Foundation', 'Building', 'Mastery'][num - 1];
  } else if (total === 4) {
    return ['Foundation', 'Building', 'Advanced', 'Mastery'][num - 1];
  } else {
    return `Phase ${num}`;
  }
}
```

## 集成到 learn:plan

在 .claude/commands/learn/plan.md 中，plan 生成后调用 assignPhases()：

```javascript
// 生成 plan 后
const { knowledgePoints, phases } = assignPhases(
  plan.knowledge_points,
  plan.dependency_graph
);

plan.knowledge_points = knowledgePoints;
plan.phases = phases;
```

